{"type":null,"faqId":43728,"title":"杂志锁屏图片更新和保存图片、订阅的方法是什么？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">默认设置是在连接WLAN时，会自动检测服务器是否有图片更新，可以手动去设置：在锁屏界面从底部向上拉，点击“更多 &gt; 设置 &gt; WLAN下自动更新内容”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">目前暂不支持手动检测，必须等待系统自己弹出提示框。需要注意的是杂志锁屏更新以后，之前的一批图片会消失，如有需要可手动点击保存，保存方法为：锁屏界面从底部向上拉，点击收藏。您如果只想下次更新喜欢的图片内容，可以在“更多 &gt; 设置 &gt; 订阅”中勾选对应的频道。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=153240\" style=\"width:1.7284722in;height:3.10625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=153241\" style=\"width:1.7368056in;height:3.11875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9229","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399375000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":9,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"杂志锁屏,图片跟新,订阅","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}